product.title: Japanese Aesthetic Tokyo Neon Lights Black Hues iPhone Case
product.body_html:
Take your phone game up a notch with one of these super dreamy cases featuring Tokyo's neon-lit streets in dark hues! Show off your love for Japan and keep your phone safe in style with these awesome designs. Keep your phone secure & stylish whether you're heading out for a party or to the office, it's perfect for any occasion. Choose between four styles.

Description:

  • High-quality TPU + IPC Cover
  • Compatible Brand: Apple iPhones
  • Function: Anti-knock. Dirt-resistant
  • Four designs available (sold individually)
  • Clear casing

A durable flexible case that grips around the edges of your phone. Made of impact-resistant TPU material with good shock absorption, protecting against drops and dents on the outer case.

Make sure you select the correct iPhone model when ordering. The phone is not sold with the phone case.


If you are interested in more items like this, please check out our website www.kawaiies.com.
